                     <interp inst="t17760221-13-off56" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17760221-13-off56" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing two black silk cloaks, value thirty-nine shillings, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17760221-13-victim174" type="victimName">
                           John
                            Crofton
                        <interp inst="t17760221-13-victim174" type="surname" value="Crofton"></interp>
